cs.CV, cs.AR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

The paper focuses on memory optimization techniques for deep neural networks and computer vision computations, which are typically categorized under computer vision (cs.CV) and augmented reality (cs.AR). The paper also discusses machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques, which are closely related to computer vision. Additionally, the paper proposes a specialized hardware unit for DNN tasks, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
